TITLE: ToDo App using React + Redux + EC2015 (ES6+)
AUTHOR: Tyler Murphy


SYNOPSIS:
This is the Redux "ToDo App", with source code from redux.js.org.


FEATURES:


FUTURE DIRECTIONS:


INSTALLATION:
1. Install dependencies:
> npm install --save react react-dom react-router@2.0.0-rc5 react-redux radium react-bootstrap react-fontawesome
> npm install --save-dev html-webpack-plugin webpack webpack-dev-server babel-core babel-loader babel-preset-react
> npm install --save-dev babel-cli babel-preset-es2015

2. Create the Dist (index.html, index_bundle.js) directory:
> npm run production

3. Run dev server on localhost:8080
> npm run start


Note: Make sure that es2015 is added to presets in the .babelrc file.
